---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Research Methodology"
  description="How Portuguese Estate researches UAE property data — sources, limitations, and partner referral policy."
>
  <section class="site-container py-12 md:py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="mb-6">Methodology</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Our guides combine publicly available regulatory sources (DLD, AMPI, ICA visa rules), market reports,
        and cross-checks against multiple listing platforms. Figures are rounded and dated — markets move quickly.
      </p>
      <h2>Sources we prioritise</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Official UAE government and emirate-level portals</li>
        <li>Licensed broker market commentary (clearly labelled as third-party)</li>
        <li>Transaction fee schedules published by land departments</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Lead referral policy</h2>
      <p>
        When you submit the shortlist form, your enquiry may be shared with a <strong>AMPI-licensed partner</strong>
        who can show regulated inventory and complete KYC. We do not sell your data to unrelated marketing lists.
      </p>
      <h2>Updates</h2>
      <p>
        Each guide shows an <em>Updated</em> date when material facts change (visa thresholds, fee changes, major market shifts).
        Always confirm numbers with your lawyer and broker before signing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
